prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration of the couple from the reference photos, transformed into cute cartoon characters. They are on a minimalist, idyllic beach with soft, pastel-colored sand and gentle turquoise waves. The woman, Lao Lao, is playfully trying to balance a comically oversized boba tea cup on her head, looking up at it with a big, happy, slightly mischievous smile. The man, Jordan, stands next to her, laughing and holding out his hands as if ready to catch the giant cup if it falls. The boba cup has a large, colorful straw and exaggerated tapioca pearls visible. The sky is a simple, soft pastel blue with a few stylized, fluffy white clouds. In the center of the card, below the couple, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The overall design is clean, minimalist, and uses a light, airy color palette, emphasizing the cute and humorous scene.
